Surf_Royal

This version of surf_royal is the hardest.
Its made for skill surf servers which have a surf timer because there is no jail in this version.

There is 1 Spawn and 5 Stages.

Spawn  - Synx & CKM
Stage1 - Synx
Stage2 - Synx
Stage3 - Synx
Stage4 - Synx & NoProx3
Stage5 - Synx
